<section class="mt-5">
    <div class="container">
        <hr class="featurette-divider">
        <div class="row mt-5">
            <div class="col-md-7">
            <h2 class="featurette-heading">PHASE I - PLAN
            <p class="lead">
                We will visit your home to perform an assesment and work with you to define the requirements of your
                home automation project.  
            </p>    
            <p class="lead">
                Once the goals are in place we can provide details about what kind of technology can help you achieve your goals 
                with a budget in mind.  
            </p>
            <p class="lead">
                Each planning phase will come with a detailed quote and action plan that can be adjusted as needed.
            </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-5">
            <img class="featurette-image img-fluid mx-auto" src="<%= asset_pack_path 'media/images/technology_blueprint.jpg' %>" data-holder-rendered="true">
            </div>
        </div>
        <hr class="featurette-divider">
        <div class="row mt-5">
            <div class="col-md-7 order-md-2">
            <h2 class="featurette-heading">PHASE II - ACTION
            <p class="lead">
                Once the final plan has been approved we will schedule a time to start installing your home automation solution.  During this process you are invited to engage
                in the process and ask as much as you want about the process.  
            </p>
            <p class="lead">
                We hold security in the highest regard when it comes to your system, therefore, we insist that you be present so that at the time of configuration you can provide the neccesary credentials to complete the install.  
                After the installation is complete we will conduct a complete test of your system to ensure that everything is operating as expected. 
            </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-5 order-md-1">
            <img class="featurette-image img-fluid mx-auto" src="<%= asset_pack_path 'media/images/tools.jpg' %> " data-src="holder.js/500x500/auto" data-holder-rendered="true">
            </div>
        </div>
        <hr class="featurette-divider">
        <div class="row mt-5">
            <div class="col-md-7">
            <h2 class="featurette-heading">PHASE III - SUPPORT
            <p class="lead">
                We want to ensure your satisfaction with your new home automation system.  Each install comes included with three months of follow up support.  We will make
                house calls as needed and provide updates to your system if needed.
            </p>
            <p class="lead">
                After three months we provide support plans at an additional cost.  With a support plan you will get periodic house visits to ensure your
                system is functioning properly, up to date, and complete with the latest security measures.
            </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-5">
            <img class="featurette-image img-fluid mx-auto" src="<%= asset_pack_path 'media/images/support.jpg' %>" data-src="holder.js/500x500/auto" alt="500x500"  data-holder-rendered="true" >
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
